    "headline": "Comstock Announces ParkX Entry Into Hospitality With Two Starbucks Locations",
    "summary": "RESTON, Va., May 01, 2026--Comstock Holding Companies, Inc. (Nasdaq: CHCI) (\"Comstock\"), a leading asset manager, developer, and operator of mixed-use and transit-oriented properties in the Washington, D.C., region, today announced that ParkX Management (\"ParkX\") has assumed management responsibilities for two separate Starbucks-licensed locations within Comstock's two premier mixed-use, transit oriented developments - Reston Station in Reston, Virginia, and Loudoun Station in Ashburn, Virginia.",
